#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.55"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.55:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.55:0.2"
msgid "6. Brāhmaṇavagga"
msgstr "6. Brahmins"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.55:0.3"
msgid "55. Nibbutasutta"
msgstr "55. Extinguished"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.55:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho jāṇussoṇi "
"brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one "
"side, and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an3.55:1.2"
msgid "“‘sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānan’ti, bho gotama, vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, they say that ‘extinguishment is realizable in this very "
"life’."

msgctxt "an3.55:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kittāvatā nu kho, bho gotama, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ hoti akālikaṃ "
"ehipassikaṃ opaneyyikaṃ paccattaṃ veditabbaṃ viññūhī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"In what way is extinguishment realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli1.159"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.55:2.1"
msgid ""
"Ratto kho, brāhmaṇa, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attabyābādhāyapi "
"ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, cetasikampi "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"“A greedy person, overcome by greed, intends to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an3.55:2.2"
msgid ""
"Rāge pahīne nevattabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na "
"ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"When greed has been given up, they don’t intend to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They don’t experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an3.55:2.3"
msgid "Evampi kho, brāhmaṇa, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is how extinguishment is realizable in this very life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.55:3.1"
msgid "Duṭṭho kho, brāhmaṇa … pe …"
msgstr "A hateful person …"

msgctxt "an3.55:3.2"
msgid ""
"mūḷho kho, brāhmaṇa, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attabyābādhāyapi "
"ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, cetasikampi "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"A deluded person, overcome by delusion, intends to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an3.55:3.3"
msgid ""
"Mohe pahīne nevattabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na "
"ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"When delusion has been given up, they don’t intend to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They don’t experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an3.55:3.4"
msgid "Evampi kho, brāhmaṇa, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This, too, is how extinguishment is realizable in this very life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: Yato kho ayaṃ, brāhmaṇa → yato ca kho ayaṃ brāhmaṇa (bj) | yato kho brāhmaṇa akālikaṃ ehipassikaṃ opaneyyikaṃ paccattaṃ veditabbaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an3.55:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yato kho ayaṃ, brāhmaṇa, anavasesaṃ rāgakkhayaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, anavasesaṃ "
"dosakkhayaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, anavasesaṃ mohakkhayaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti;"
msgstr ""
"When you experience the ending of greed, hate, and delusion without anything "
"left over,"

msgctxt "an3.55:4.2"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ hoti akālikaṃ ehipassikaṃ "
"opaneyyikaṃ paccattaṃ veditabbaṃ viññūhī”ti."
msgstr ""
"that’s how extinguishment is realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.55:5.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "an3.55:5.2"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.55:5.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
